Python Code:
Method 0: Using String Character Extraction
n=input()
sum=0
for i in n:
    sum=sum+int(i)
print(sum)
output:
23-->2+3
5
Method 1: Using Brute Force
n=int(input())
sum=0
while(n!=0):
    d=n%10
    sum+=d
    n=n//10
print(sum)
output:
23-->2+3
5

Cpp Code:
Method 1
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
  int n,sum=0;
  cin>>n;
  while(n!=0)
  {
    int d=n%10;
    sum+=d;
    n=n/10;
  }
  cout<<sum;
}
output:
23-->2+3
5


